{"tid":499209,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【年尾無情雞】傳和記電訊裁數十名IT員工","createTime":"2017-12-14T14:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T16:00:27.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6d63231e8701b75c28033cc82e213bc2bea8ae","tid":499209,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:04:41.000Z","msg":"踏入12月，一眾打工仔本來期待派完花紅好過年，但和記電訊（215）員工可能冇咁好彩啦，年尾慘食無情雞。有和電員工向《蘋果》報料指，今日早上開始，在和電青衣總部出現大裁員，涉及數十名員工，當中更包括一些坐房的中層，甚至「成條team剷」起，入房收大信封後更加是要即走，冇得留低。<br />\n<br />\n該名員工指，自己雖然未有未裁，但擔心隨時會被叫入房收信封。又指，不少同事都有家庭，年尾被裁對其生活做成很大壓力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171214/57581711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57581711&d=A1ULU37iwBzk0xgqJ3kRS6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=2f6ed5b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57581711&h=d3b55813\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171214/57581711</a>"},{"pid":"24b39ef91bf86f7f45d9c0168dedd6f9ccf9f43e","tid":499209,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dcada8b64a6ce518c785983cb70d5b76f70405","tid":499209,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"坐房的中層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ff8f66ce1512cd06daaa08ebe3dfb26ab3f28a","tid":499209,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"邊度有寫IT狗？"},{"pid":"ea598407bdedd6409d2dc05c0111c7e1407930f6","tid":499209,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0